<item>
            <title>[LU-11917] sanity test_258a: error, failed to take i_mutex, rc=0</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11917</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger  &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3776c5be-2595-11e9-b901-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3776c5be-2595-11e9-b901-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_258a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;error, failed to take i_mutex, rc=0
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It looks like this is fallout from the MDS still being in recovery after the end of test:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[ 6424.571441] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark == sanity test 258a: ================================================================================= 02:00:07 \(1548727207\)
[ 6424.696176] Lustre: lustre-MDT0000: Recovery over after 0:01, of 2 clients 1 recovered and 7 were evicted.
[ 6424.773262] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == sanity test 258a: ================================================================================= 02:00:07 (1548727207)
[ 6425.055810] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  sanity test_258a: @@@@@@ FAIL: error, failed to take i_mutex, rc=0 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;





&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_258a - error, failed to take i_mutex, rc=0&lt;/p&gt;</description>
